short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Allows use of the EyeBankWeb plugin

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: IrisGuard EyeBank Web Extension: This extensions allows web users to connect to the IrisGuard iris imagers and perform the standard EyeBank library calls from chrome. The calls include: Recognition, Enrollment, Modification and Deletion.
